# Formatting

After editing files, run Prettier to ensure consistent formatting:

```bash
npx prettier --write <changed files>
```

Prettier config is in `.prettierrc`. It uses double quotes, trailing commas, 100 char width, and 4-space indentation.

Prettier does not support Dockerfile, `.env`, or justfile — skip those.
